Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Smallpox eradicated
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0409pgs
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Dec 1977
UN's World Health Organisation announces smallpox has been eradicated from everywhere in the world. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less